        " : سَأَلْتُهُ عَنْ رَجُلٍ أَوْصَى بِجُزْءٍ مِنْ مَالِهِ قَالَ \"سُبُعُ ثُلُثِهِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5477 - It is narrated by Al-Bazanti from Al-Husayn ibn Khalid, who said:\nI asked Abu Al-Hasan (as) about a man who bequeathed a portion of his wealth.\nImam (as) replied: \"It is one-seventh of his one-third share.\""
        ]
